Individual




Ashok N. Bakhru



Mr. Ashok N. Bakhru is Chairman at Goldman Sachs ETF Trust, Chairman at Goldman Sachs MLP Income Opportunities Fund, Chairman at Goldman Sachs BDC, Inc., Chairman at Goldman Sachs Trust, Chairman at Goldman Sachs Credit Strategies Fund, Chairman at Goldman Sachs Variable Insurance Trust, and Chairman at Goldman Sachs Trust II. He is on the Board of Directors at Investment Company Institute, Goldman Sachs MLP & Energy Renaissance Fund, Institute for Higher Education Policy, Mutual Fund Directors Forum, and Independent Directors Council.
Mr. Bakhru was previously employed as a Director & Executive Officer by Apollo Capital Management LP, Independent Director by Apollo Investment Corp., President by ABN Associates LLC, Chairman by The Goldman Sachs Group, Inc., Chief Financial & Administrative Officer by Coty, Inc., and Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Scott Paper Co. He also served on the board at Arkwright Mutual Insurance Co., Cornell University, Private Equity Investors Ill LP, and Private Equity Investors IV LP.



